Interpretation 1: Just filter/display a different city's data\
If the data has already been researched and verified, switching the widget to show Milan vs Seville vs Barcelona is trivial \'97 maybe an hour's work. It would just be a city selector at the top that swaps the dataset being rendered. The hard work is the research, not the display.\
Interpretation 2: Actually run the three-phase research process for any city entered\
This is the interesting one, and it's substantially more complex. The widget would need to:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls50\ilvl0\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Accept a city input from the user\
\ls50\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Run Phase 1\'963 searches to find relevant publications and writers for that city\
\ls50\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Fetch each source article\
\ls50\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Extract restaurant names from the fetched text\
\ls50\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Look up Google Maps place IDs for each restaurant\
\ls50\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Build and render the cards\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 The core challenge is that steps 2\'965 require Claude \'97 they involve judgment calls about which sources are credible, reading and interpreting article text, and disambiguating restaurant names. A static HTML widget can't do any of that on its own.\
The realistic path would be to use the Anthropic API inside the widget \'97 essentially "Claude in Claude." The widget would send the city name to the API, which would run the research pipeline and return structured JSON (restaurant name, neighbourhood, sources, quotes, place IDs), and the widget would render the results. This is technically possible and something we've discussed for the broader LocalBite app.\
The honest complexity breakdown:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls51\ilvl0\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
