\ls51\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Prompting Claude to reliably follow the three-phase approach and return clean structured JSON: significant (several days of iteration)\
\ls51\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Handling edge cases \'97 cities with few English sources, paywalled articles, JS-rendered pages, ambiguous restaurant names: ongoing\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 The fetch step is the hardest constraint. Claude running inside the widget can call the Anthropic API, but it can't directly call 
