\ls81\ilvl0\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Time Out entries confirmed by at least one other source should be included without hesitation\
\ls81\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Time Out-only entries should be treated with the same caution as a partial fetch \'97 include only if the quote is genuinely substantive and the restaurant is clearly not a tourist trap\
\ls81\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Add a transparency note to the city pack JSON indicating that Time Out is a global brand rather than a local writer\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
