Where will the JSON files live? If you're comfortable creating a free GitHub account and repository, that's the cleanest path \'97 it gives you public URLs for the JSON files, free hosting for the HTML viewer, and version control for everything. If you'd prefer to keep it local for now, we build the viewer to load from the same folder and convert to GitHub later.\
Which feels right?\
