\cf2 Good choices. Given the content spans Mediterranean Europe and North Africa \'97 Barcelona, Valencia, Fes, Marrakesh \'97 I'd choose a warm terracotta as the primary accent. It works across all four cities without feeling too Spanish or too Moroccan, and it reads as food-related and inviting without being clich\'e9d. It also pairs well with warm off-white backgrounds and dark charcoal text, which is the right combination for a card-based travel tool.\
\
