\
Immediate fixes worth doing now\
1. Test all four cities \'97 switch through Barcelona, Valencia, Fes, and Marrakesh in the dropdown and check that cards render correctly, filters populate, and the MAD pricing shows properly for Morocco cities. Note anything that looks wrong and we'll fix it in one pass.\
