\fs32 \cf2 What this means for your Pro plan specifically:\
On Claude Pro you don't pay per token \'97 but the rate limit is effectively a token quota. Extended thinking consumes that quota 2-5x faster than standard mode. This is exactly why the Barcelona v4 run hit the rate limit before the export step.\
Practical recommendation for your use case:\
For simple queries or creative generation tasks, you're paying for capabilities you won't use.
