\cf2 \cb5 Excluding Google, are there any alternatives for geocoding to Nominatim and Foursquare that we should consider for this project and if so, what are the alternatives' advantages and disadvantages compared to Nominatim and Foursquare?\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs24 \cf6 Mar 26
\fs32 \cf4 \
\
\
\
