\fs32 \cf2 My recommendation for LocalBite\
Immediate improvement \'97 add Photon as a second free attempt after Nominatim. Same data, different algorithm, no setup cost, likely 5-10% improvement in hit rate. This is a 1-hour addition to the geocoding script.\
For European city batches \'97 test Mapbox. The proximity bias feature is cleaner than bounding boxes, the free tier is generous, and European coverage is strong. One test on Lisbon would tell us if it meaningfully outperforms Nominatim.\
Keep Foursquare in the script but don't rely on it. It costs nothing to try and occasionally might find something the others miss.\
For Morocco specifically \'97 accept that automated geocoding will always have a 30-40% miss rate regardless of which free service you use. The medinas are simply not well enough mapped in any open dataset to achieve the hit rates we see in European cities. Manual Google Maps lookup remains the right fallback for Moroccan cities.\
The practical sequence for the geocoding script would be:\
