\fs32 \cf2 My recommendation on which to test first\
Start with Combination 1. It costs nothing beyond time, covers both Morocco and Europe, and gives us real data on whether Photon and Overpass add meaningful value over Nominatim alone. If the combined hit rate reaches 80%+ for European cities then Combination 2 is unnecessary \'97 we have a fully free solution that's good enough.\
