The real argument for Mapbox in a batch context is reliability and native confidence scores \'97 not hit rate. Commercial services (HERE, Mapbox) are more reliable for unattended overnight runs than community-run services (Nominatim, Photon, Overpass) which can have intermittent slowdowns.\
