\fs36 \cf2 STRATEGY B \'97 Writer-First Emphasis (6 pre-mapping + 30 standard = 36 total)\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs32 \cf2 Purpose\
Test whether a dedicated writer discovery phase before the main search plan surfaces meaningfully different and better sources than the standard structured approach. The pre-mapping phase is the variable being tested \'97 everything else mirrors Strategy A as closely as possible.\
Pre-mapping phase (6 queries \'97 run before writing search plan)\
These 6 searches run before any other searches. For each result that returns a named writer, immediately fetch their most recent Lisbon restaurant article via Jina and extract the writer's name, publication, and URL before proceeding. The search plan is then written with known writers already in hand.\
Pre-mapping query 1: 
\fs28\fsmilli14400 \cf7 \cb8 food writers Lisbon Portugal local guide 2026
\fs32 \cf2 \cb1  Pre-mapping query 2: 
