Before committing to building and testing Strategy C, it's worth asking whether the test is worth running on Lisbon again (a third time) or whether we have enough understanding to simply write Strategy C into the next city prompt and observe how it performs on Porto.\
Porto would be a natural test \'97 it's the next Portuguese city, it's well-documented, and running Strategy C there with the new rules would tell us whether the combined approach works without spending another session on Lisbon.\
