\fs32 \cf2 This means for production use beyond testing LocalBite would need a paid plan. Their cheapest paid plan is approximately \'8015/month. For a hobby project this is a real cost consideration.\
3 \'97 Photon may be sufficient without any commercial service\
The Photon results \'97 64% for Marrakesh, 72% for Lisbon \'97 combined with manual verification, may be acceptable for LocalBite's scale. At 36-62 restaurants per city, the manual workload difference between Photon (10 lookups) and a theoretical OpenCage result is perhaps 3-5 lookups per city. Whether that's worth a paid subscription or the complexity of an API key dependency is a judgment call.\
4 \'97 HERE must be removed from the Lisbon JSON\
