This is the definitive answer directly from LocationIQ's own documentation:\
"You can store the output forever but there are restrictions on caching data based on your account with us. Caching refers to storing request-response pairs with the intention of not hitting LocationIQ endpoints. If you're on the free plan, we allow caching for up to 48 hours."
