LocationIQ is legally clean for LocalBite. HERE is not.\
The earlier concern about the 48-hour cache limit is now fully resolved \'97 that applies only to storing request-response pairs (caching to avoid re-querying the API), not to storing the coordinate values themselves, which are explicitly permitted forever.\
