Is the radius (1km, 2km, 5km) calibrated correctly for how dense a city pack is \'97 Toronto at ~50 restaurants spread across a large city will feel very different from Chefchaouen at 17 restaurants in a 500m medina\
\ls501\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Does the interaction feel natural when you're physically somewhere and want to know what's nearby\
\ls501\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Does tapping the map to set an origin point feel intuitive on mobile\
\ls501\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
