\cf2 All of these translate directly to other cities. The radius calibration question is especially important \'97 a 1km radius in Chefchaouen captures the entire restaurant pack, while 1km in Toronto might capture 3 restaurants. The UI needs to communicate this gracefully rather than showing "0 results" when the radius is too tight.\
